description: Amundi US Treasury Bond 7-10Y UCITS ETF EUR Hedged Acc seeks to replicate, as closely as possible the performance of the Bloomberg US Treasury 7-10 Year Index (the “Benchmark Index"), denominated in USD, whether the trend is rising or falling while minimizing the volatility of the di?erence between the return of the Sub-Fund and the return of the Index (the “Tracking Error”). For further information on index rules, please refer to the fund prospectus or KID.
name: Amundi US Treasury Bond 7-10Y UCITS ETF EUR Hedged Acc
